F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3rFubmZiI8RVmJ45oYX4swiZJ77juyfi09Ngx4juJ-R5cPkth_4y_Sh2A&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUrAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=287812c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FUACVWYQVWBCODLNEIICK7ICBVE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3rFubmZiI8RVmJ45oYX4swiZJ77juyfi09Ngx4juJ-R5cPkth_4y_Sh2A&h=aa257147\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/UACVWYQVWBCODLNEIICK7ICBVE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3rFubmZiI8RVmJ45oYX4swiZJ77juyfi09Ngx4juJ-R5cPkth_4y_Sh2A</a><br />\n<br />\n第四波武肺疫情持續擴散，沙田及觀塘一田百貨超市早前有多名員工確診，超市其後要求員工上班前進行武肺測試。《蘋果》收到崇光百貨內部電郵，指本月29日起，所有在崇光百貨超市工作的兼職及全職員工，必須在上班前向超市經理提交24小時內的武肺病毒檢測陰性結果及收據，並每14日就需要重新檢測一次。有員工就透露，若上班前未能出示檢測結果，將不能在超市工作。<br />\n<br />\n兼職或全職員工均須「強制檢測」<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫情在社區擴散，又有不少隱性傳播鏈，街市、超市等人流多的地方，爆發武肺的風險大增。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》收到一封崇光百貨的內部電郵，指近日有超市出現確診個案，而政府曾指在超市工作的員工屬高風險。為了及早預防、識別無徵狀的患者，以及保障員工向顧客的健康，由本月29日起，所有在崇光超市SOGO Freshmart工作的員工必須提交武肺病毒檢測陰性結果，並須向公司出示收據以作證明。<br />\n電郵內容又稱，所有在超市工作的職員，不論是兼職或全職員工均要進行「強制檢測」。員工亦需向超市經理提交上班前24小時內進行的武肺病毒檢測陰性結果及收據，並每14日就要重新檢測一次。<br />\n<br />\n只接受上班前24小時內之檢測結果<br />\n<br />\n在崇光超市工作的員工向《蘋果》透露，公司只接受上班前24小時內的檢測結果，若未能出示相關證明，將不能在超市工作，「威脅我哋冇報告就唔畀返工，仲要每兩星期做一次檢測，太過嚴格。」<br />\n<br />\n該員工又批評，超市一直未有禁止客人在超市內進食，「又話超市工作係高風險，但一直都無禁止或者阻止客人除口罩喺超市入面食嘢，就算我哋做咗檢測，呢刻冇事，但啲客唔戴口罩食嘢，都係增加我哋中招風險。」"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"辭職囉，做就收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b55b6f97fdde22617c937737e0c534391c2a09","tid":2341549,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:53:39.000Z","msg":"藍店"},{"pid":"82e9255b0e5a21fca72197391ddcba1999f08077","tid":2341549,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:54:11.000Z","msg":"個鼻仲使要？"},{"pid":"7835efc0e2515106c4e344906f6dc11afa4c01d8","tid":2341549,"uid":224856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"超市就要驗，其他樓層就唔洗。"},{"pid":"38411a01d933fb39418c74b24f696bbf18bf5e39","tid":2341549,"uid":318807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7835efc0e2515106c4e344906f6dc11afa4c01d8","tid":2341549,"uid":224856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"超市就要驗，其他樓層就唔洗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:57:21.000Z","msg":"係呀所以先覺得on9"},{"pid":"eec41b0c3c600bb07ff3f3139b757f752422c5b9","tid":2341549,"uid":224856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:59:07.000Z","msg":"真係估唔到尋日講，今日就上報，抵死！😂😂😂"},{"pid":"78f0e7adbe33d4913145e66173cb0ae9182452af","tid":2341549,"uid":21409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"727582f473644d7e34067dd66493fff61d07c644","tid":2341549,"uid":260694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe586ea2df541371ce92d594fe0a3081f7a1c0a","tid":2341549,"uid":21409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:52:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/UACVWYQVWBCODLNEIICK7ICBVE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3rFubmZiI8RVmJ45oYX4swiZJ77juyfi09Ngx4juJ-R5cPkth_4y_Sh2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FUACVWYQVWBCODLNEIICK7ICBVE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3rFubmZiI8RVmJ45oYX4swiZJ77juyfi09Ngx4juJ-R5cPkth_4y_Sh2A&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUrAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=287812c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FUACVWYQVWBC